# MCP

Configured in `.cursor/mcp.json`:
- `shadcn` — official registry reference (`npx shadcn@latest mcp`)
- `shacdn` — project export server (`mcp/shacdn-server`)
- `filesystem` — repo-scoped file tools (when enabled)

## Rules
- Prefer project MCP for exporting SCSS components to other apps
- Prefer official shadcn MCP for registry parity checks
- Do not point MCP at absolute machine-specific paths in committed config
- If `mcp/shacdn-server/dist` is missing: build that package (bootstrap attempts this)
- See also `shacdn-mcp.mdc` and `shadcn-mcp-reference.mdc`
